    • create_ContactTracer

      public void create_ContactTracer​(Citizen citizen)
      Creates a new ContactTracer object. It stores the account's PersonalDetails into a temporary variable, deletes the account from the ArrayList, then instantiatess the new Contact Tracer with the same username and password while also assigning the PersonalDetails.
      Parameters:
      citizen - - the Citizen object to be remade into a ContactTracer.

    • terminate_Account

      public void terminate_Account​(Citizen citizen)

    • addCase

      public static void addCase​(Citizen citizen, java.time.LocalDate date, int caseNumber, java.lang.String status, java.lang.String tracerUsername)
      Adds a new case for all Government Officials to see. A case is added whenever a Citizen declares themselves positive by being tested.
      Parameters:
      citizen - - the Citizen who is positive.
      date - - the date that the case has been noted.
      caseNumber - - the case number that will be assigned.
      status - - the status of the case for Contact Tracers to distinguish between a case being "Traced" or "Untraced"
      tracerUsername - - the Contact Tracer's username assigned to the case.
